FBIS4-15715 "drsov069_u_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-069 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 Latvia Ulmanis Refuses To Sign Withdrawal Documents Ulmanis Refuses To Sign Withdrawal Documents LD0804125794 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 1200 GMT 8 Apr 94 LD0804125794 Moscow Russian Television Network Russian BFN [From the "Vesti" newscast] [Text] [Announcer Aleksandr Sapozhnikov] Latvian President Ulmanis, speaking on national radio, said that under the present circumstances, he was not ready to sign the Latvian-Russian agreements on conditions for the pullout of [Russian] troops. He added that he did not consider it possible to sign those documents on the agreed date of 20 April.
